item.title: Vimeo holiday special & other great videos
item.description: We (the Vimeo Staff) just released the 2013 Vimeo Holiday Special, embedded below. (and I have a line in it! "Who's behind this?") Here's last year's Holiday video which is just as cool. Not a lot of people know this but we actually produce a bunch of our own videos. Some of my favorites include Auto-tuning, Idea, Vimeo goes bowling, Vimeo production reel 2012, Open your eyes to the new vimeo and Brad!
